<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="take-care">take care</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-that">1.★ <strong>［单独使用、接不定式或that从句］注意；当心：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Take care! You may get lost.
当心！你会迷路的。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Take care not to wake the boy.
当心别弄醒那个男孩。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Take care that you don’t slip on the icy roads.
注意不要在结了冰的路上滑倒。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[告别用语] 珍重；保重：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Bye! Take care!
再见，多保重！</p></div></div>